{"tid":1745282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真，投票好緊要，但監票更重要","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:59:16.000Z","uid":235015,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49a59b1a43fe9ccfe1570382d9ff309186cbad3a","tid":1745282,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"見到宜家都冇post講監票<br />\n中港共一定唔會係投票果陣做野，或者已經種哂票，但一定點票監票果陣做假做獲勁既<br />\n所以我地好需要討論下監票流程，點樣監票，有咩權利<br />\n<br />\n利申唔識，希望有識既人可以開post講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝都有個雲海既舊片post出左黎，真係一定會係點票到做手腳架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aae9489df0f81f0ee55b757c1ce9a047f591b01","tid":1745282,"uid":202267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:11:34.000Z","msg":"tui<br />\n大家有時間既 去睇埋點票! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7cd4413cbfd3a58a80c1e7aebae4bf944f23aa","tid":1745282,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"監點/監投代理人一早報晒名架啦<br />\n佢地識做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n普通市民都可以去睇點票，不過冇得反對"},{"pid":"f69555402bfc5d76673f6263aab036c2e2e93a8d","tid":1745282,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"實出拿渣招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473051bca86cd645dee7a4a88a77f46abebaddb7","tid":1745282,"uid":210122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"推!!<br />\n<br />\n呢樣好重要!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru